{
  "text": "Now, the animal in second density is composed of light, as are all things. What I'm trying to get at is the relationship between the light that the various bodies of the animal are created of, and the relationship of this to the energy centers which are active and the ones which are not active, and how this is linked with the logos. It is a difficult question to ask. Can you give me some kind of answer on that? I am wrong. The will of the logos posits the potentials available to the evolving entity, the will of the entity as it evolves is the single measure of the rate and fastidiousness of the activation and balancing of the various energy centers.",
